metadata.name: AIDENTITY
metadata.description:
AIDENTITY

Dots and lines in the front layer trace the background layer in synchronized movements with the music.

This represents the AI trying to understand human history and culture and find its identity as Artificial Intelligence. The dots and lines also represent the nodes and transactions of the blockchain.

I aimed to represent the overlap of both the Industrial Revolution in modern history and the Information Revolution we are experiencing across time.
